## `test_empty_file_has_zero_chunks(fs_with_file)`
<!-- checksum: placeholder-blobs-11 -->

### Purpose
A freshly created file with no writes has `size == 0` and zero rows in `blobs`. Empty files are NOT represented by an empty-row placeholder.

### Postconditions

```python
fs, fd = fs_with_file
assert fs.stat("/f").size == 0
assert fs._count_chunks(fs.stat("/f").inode) == 0
assert fs.read(fd, size=100, offset=0) == b""
```

